      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to enjoy the ride in this wonderful find! This vehicle is in good condition, clearly showing it has been well-maintained and cared for over the years. It drives smoothly and looks great, making it a reliable and stylish choice for your next adventure. It's a fantastic value for anyone looking for quality and dependability!",
