    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from major mechanical failures, including a non-starting engine and a transmission that requires a full rebuild. The exterior has significant rust, several deep dents, and peeling clear coat, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is best suited for an experienced mechanic looking for a donor vehicle or a very intensive long-term restoration project.",
